Class Board

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.elements.Board

  • public class Board
extends java.lang.Object
    Typical board is an arrayList of squares This class is a container that holds squares, cards and figures informations and provides a number of procedures that are necessary for monopoly logic to work.
